{
  "id": "CHAR_eldric_vitrane",
  "label": "Eldric Vitrane",
  "description": "This individual constitutes an undead remnant endemic to the Vitrified Rift, preserved by heat-scorched desiccation and the glass-fused injuries characteristic of that hazard zone. Brown eyes sit deep in a skull-tight face, while black hair persists in sparse, brittle lengths against a pale_green complexion. The frame is narrow and angular, with rigid posture and joints set in habitual, grinding angles that indicate long-term reanimation rather than recent death. Their manner is fixated and iterative, governed by rote impulses and an unyielding attraction to rift-light and exposed heat-sheen.",
